{"tid":220302,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[又炒車] 2港女立山黑部No Show真相！網民：大家怪錯港女","createTime":"2017-04-28T00:26:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-28T06:40:05.000Z","uid":23707,"like":20,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"840bc0beceda70c04af578f68ae51889b3247ea9","tid":220302,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T00:26:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/topic/detail.html?id=ABFGD1owBwlZHwNv&amp;p=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Ftopic%2Fdetail.html%3Fid%3DABFGD1owBwlZHwNv%26p%3D1&d=ulKCtXgG4rwmRR8qyGKIuUbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=ccd0d7a7\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/topic/detail.html?id=ABFGD1owBwlZHwNv&amp;p=1</a><br />\n<br />\n事件過了半天，日本方面與入境處實證兩名港女正身處安全地方。有報道指罵她們「No Show」失蹤驚動日本警方浪費警力。追查原因，原來是她們訂了「雷鳥莊」旅館，但因未能預期到達到旅館，所以在黃昏時段發Email給訂購的旅行社交代，之後便中斷訊號。唯旅行社未能通知旅館，晚上9:30亦未見蹤影，才報警形成今次誤會發生。"},{"pid":"6c18a5d6d6323438ecd6d2e3485373ae17e7c3b9","tid":220302,"uid":29784,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T00:33:56.000Z","msg":"連登垃圾又炒車"},{"pid":"2836096a0e456c40127d94f14c1d21bbc2ab4e68","tid":220302,"uid":32655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T00:34:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13e4e58ae1f0d77e25d8b3ff4156dbc2ef54a656","tid":220302,"uid":882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T00:38:36.000Z","msg":"邊間Agent?"},{"pid":"299345dc7d5af0840364460271325c4a37d7a807","tid":220302,"uid":882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T00:39:07.000Z","msg":"呢d情況 屌Agent la"},{"pid":"c49e39851bea6ae7dfdbd5283ee11d11bc6f78a6","tid":220302,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T00:39:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>連登垃圾又炒車</blockquote>班踩港支那狗又炒車就真"},{"pid":"ce1e034bffae09b079624ebb464d200ebac202e0","tid":220302,"uid":51747,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":